text_raw:
2. The 17th day of October 2024 is appointed as the day on which the Motor 
Insurance Insolvency Compensation Act 2024 (No. 32 of 2024) shall come into 
operation. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

16 October, 2024. 

JACK CHAMBERS, 

Minister for Finance. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
"Iris Oifigiúil" of 18th October, 2024.
